 50 cm<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:\" arial\",sans-serif\"=\"\">                            Karpfen......... 32 cm<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:\" arial\",sans-serif\"=\"\">                            Schleie......... 25 cm<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:\" arial\",sans-serif\"=\"\">                            Zander.......... 40 cm<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:\r\n\" arial\",sans-serif\"=\"\">                            Für\r\nnicht genannte Fische gelten die gesetzlichen <br>\r\n                            Mindestmaße lt.\r\nNds. Fischereigesetz.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:\r\n\" arial\",sans-serif\"=\"\"> </span><u><span style=\"font-family:\r\n\" arial\",sans-serif\"=\"\">Schonzeiten:</span></u><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">      Barsch, Forelle, Hecht und Zander</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">vom\r\n1. Januar bis 30. April eines jeden Jahres</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:\r\n\" arial\",sans-serif\"=\"\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Es sind die gesetzlichen Bestimmungen zu beachten!</span></p>","rules_files":[{"id":534061,"name":"angelsportverein-hage-e-v-bestimmungen","description":null,"file":"https://api.hejfish.com/files/download/ebb72419ba32aff8ab831928fd47fc342b42972a/angelsportverein-hage-e-v-bestimmungen.pdf"},{"id":534062,"name":"angelsportverein-hage-e-v-bestimmungen","description":null,"file":"https://api.hejfish.com/files/download/67a35379e4ee0395cf2919049797853db8b505d0/angelsportverein-hage-e-v-bestimmungen.pdf"},{"id":534063,"name":"angelsportverein-hage-e-v-bestimmungen","description":null,"file":"https://api.hejfish.com/files/download/23e071ac941c15fa5501dbb6a6d2963f7d8b5bb5/angelsportverein-h